These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, apricot, white, azure
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, motorbike, airplane, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is not to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##8
2. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person who likes green##1
3. the person who likes apricot is on the left or right of the person who likes white##3
4. the person who likes azure is somewhere to the right of the person driving the motorbike##5
5. the person who likes azure is not to the left of the person driving the taxi##8
6. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the left of the person who likes apricot##5
7. the person who likes apricot is somewhere between the person who likes green and the person driving the motorbike##7
8. the person who likes apricot and the person driving the taxi have the same parity positions##9
9. the person who likes white and the person driving the quad-bike have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Nationality   | green | apricot | white     | azure |
| Pet           | airplane   | taxi     | motorbike | quad-bike  |

