.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-2::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, metal, punk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, july, october, september
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's birthday is in september and the fan dubstep have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's birthday is in july is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##8
4. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the right of the fan punk##8
5. the person who's birthday is in december is somewhere to the left of the fan classical##5
6. the fan classical is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
7. the fan dubstep is somewhere to the right of the fan classical##5
8. the fan punk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |      3      |     4     |
| Beverage   | punk     | metal    | classical | dubstep    |
| Hobby      | december | july | october      | september |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-3::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, writing, skydiving, photography
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, lavender, white, amber
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is somewhere to the left of the person who likes white##5
2. the person who likes red is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
6. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who likes red##1
7. the person who likes red is not to the left of the person who likes lavender##8
8. the person who's hobby is writing and the person who likes lavender have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3     |   4   |
| Beverage   | writing    | skydiving   | baking    | photography  |
| Food       | lavender | amber | red | white |

