.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-4::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, bongani, baccarat, dunhill
City: miami, london, boston, new-york
1. the person traveling to miami is the bongani-smoker##1
2. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
3. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the left of the bongani-smoker##5
4. the person traveling to new-york is on the left or right of the baccarat-smoker##3
5. the person traveling to london is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
6. the dunhill-smoker and the person traveling to new-york have the same parity positions##9
7. the baccarat-smoker is on the left or right of the davidoff-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |       2        |   3    |     4      |
| Job           | dunhill | baccarat | davidoff  | bongani |
| Music-Genre   | boston             | london          | new-york | miami    |

