.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, drawing, skydiving, singing
The people use 4 different means of transport: subway, jet-ski, train, quad-bike
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is not the person driving the train##6
2. the person driving the subway and the person who's hobby is video-games have different parity positions##9
3. the person driving the jet-ski and the person who's hobby is drawing have different parity positions##9
4. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##5
5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
7. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
8. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
9. the person driving the quad-bike is not the person who's hobby is singing##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | video-games | skydiving | singing  | drawing |
| Pet           | jet-ski   | subway     | train | quad-bike      |

