5. the person playing poker and the person who likes lilac have different parity positions##9
6. the person who likes purple is not to the left of the person playing whist##8
7. the person who likes white is somewhere to the left of the person playing whist##5
8. the person playing bridge is not to the right of the person who likes white##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
