2. the person who's birthday is in november is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in december##2
3. the person who's birthday is in november and the person eating spinach have different parity positions##9
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person eating spinach is not to the right of the person eating asparagus##8
