4. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the person who likes blue##3
5. the person who likes green is on the left or right of the fan reggae##3
6. the fan salsa is on the far left##1
7. the fan blues is on the left of the person who likes orange##1
8. the person who likes blood-red is the fan metal##1
9. the person who likes green and the fan blues have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | blue   | green    | orange | blood-red    |
| Nationality   | salsa | blues | reggae   | metal |

