.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, turkish, brazilian, dutch
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, coach, designer, social-worker
 1. the dutch is on the left of the security-guard##1
 2. the designer is on the left of the coach##1
 3. the social-worker is not to the right of the designer##8
 4. the coach is in an odd position##4
 5. the security-guard is not the turkish##6
 6. the dutch is not to the right of the polish##8
 7. the dutch and the coach have the same parity positions##9
 8. the turkish is not to the right of the brazilian##8
 9. the dutch is the coach##1
10. the turkish and the coach have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | turkish    | brazilian        | dutch   | polish      |
| Hobby      | social-worker | designer | coach | security-guard |

 